article.description: — Moses Flowers had 20 points as Hartford edged past Fairfield 66-61 on Wednesday night.
article.headline: Flowers scores 20 to lift Hartford over Fairfield 66-61
article.linkText: Flowers scores 20 to lift Hartford over Fairfield 66-61
article.story: FAIRFIELD, Conn. -- — Moses Flowers had 20 points as Hartford edged past Fairfield 66-61 on Wednesday night. Hunter Marks had 13 points and seven rebounds for Hartford (1-2). Austin Williams added 12 points and seven rebounds. Caleb Green had 15 points for the Stags (0-2). Supreme Cook added 13 points and nine rebounds. Taj Benning had 13 points. Jesus Cruz had 10 points and 11 rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
